Dialogue: 1,0:00:23.08,0:00:24.71,JP-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,静留ちゃん言い方
Dialogue: 1,0:00:24.71,0:00:26.19,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,ねえ　あたし玲実
Dialogue: 1,0:00:26.19,0:00:28.26,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,あたしのこと玲実って呼んでね
Dialogue: 1,0:00:28.26,0:00:29.36,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,あ　まんまか
Dialogue: 1,0:00:29.36,0:00:31.37,JP-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,正式名称は零点玲実
Dialogue: 1,0:00:31.37,0:00:32.47,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,全然違う
Dialogue: 1,0:00:32.47,0:00:34.35,JP-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,中富さんびっくりしちゃったよね
Dialogue: 1,0:00:34.58,0:00:36.03,JP-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,怖がらなくていいよ
