Comment: 1,0:02:13.50,0:02:15.50,JP-Main-Down,,0,0,0,,正文
Dialogue: 1,0:02:15.50,0:02:18.52,JP-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,皆さんは東吾野の方ですか
Dialogue: 1,0:02:18.52,0:02:19.63,JP-Main-Down,Keiko,0,0,0,,そうです
Dialogue: 1,0:02:19.63,0:02:21.14,JP-Main-Down,Keiko,0,0,0,,これは電車ですか
Dialogue: 1,0:02:21.14,0:02:22.36,JP-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,はい　電車です
Dialogue: 1,0:02:22.36,0:02:24.31,JP-Main-Down,Keiko,0,0,0,,さしぶりに見ます
Dialogue: 1,0:02:24.31,0:02:26.70,JP-Main-Down,Keiko,0,0,0,,皆さんはどちらからいらしたんですか
Dialogue: 1,0:02:27.13,0:02:28.53,JP-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,隣の吾野からです
Dialogue: 1,0:02:28.86,0:02:30.06,JP-Main-Down,Resident,0,0,0,,吾野だって
Dialogue: 1,0:02:30.41,0:02:31.92,JP-Main-Down,Resident,0,0,0,,吾野が
Dialogue: 1,0:02:32.37,0:02:33.78,JP-Main-Down,Keiko,0,0,0,,それはそれは
Dialogue: 1,0:02:33.78,0:02:35.95,JP-Main-Down,Keiko,0,0,0,,今となっては遠いところから
Dialogue: 1,0:02:35.95,0:02:37.71,JP-Main-Down,Keiko,0,0,0,,大変だったでしょう
Dialogue: 1,0:02:37.71,0:02:39.46,JP-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,はあ　まあ
Dialogue: 1,0:02:39.46,0:02:41.51,JP-Main-Down,Keiko,0,0,0,,吾野の皆さんはお元気ですか
Dialogue: 1,0:02:42.23,0:02:44.95,JP-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,元気っちゃ元気かな
Dialogue: 1,0:02:44.95,0:02:46.39,JP-Main-Down,Keiko,0,0,0,,ぜひ培養
Dialogue: 1,0:02:46.39,0:02:49.81,JP-Main-Down,Keiko,0,0,0,,いいえ　施与していかれてはいかがです
Dialogue: 1,0:02:49.81,0:02:54.07,JP-Main-Down,Keiko,0,0,0,,幸い東吾野は　人間が少なくなる一方で
Dialogue: 1,0:02:54.07,0:02:55.92,JP-Main-Down,Keiko,0,0,0,,家ならいくらでも空いてますから
Dialogue: 1,0:02:55.92,0:02:57.36,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,うわ　助かる
Dialogue: 1,0:02:57.36,0:02:57.98,JP-Main-Down,Keiko,0,0,0,,ぜひ
Dialogue: 1,0:02:57.98,0:02:58.72,JP-Main-up,Resident,0,0,0,,そうだよ
Dialogue: 1,0:02:58.22,0:02:59.24,JP-Main-Down,Resident,0,0,0,,それがいい
Dialogue: 1,0:02:59.24,0:03:02.45,JP-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,でも私たちお金が余りないんです
Dialogue: 1,0:03:02.45,0:03:04.45,JP-Main-Down,Keiko,0,0,0,,そんなことはおきになさらず
Dialogue: 1,0:03:04.45,0:03:05.36,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,やっだ
Dialogue: 1,0:03:05.36,0:03:07.06,JP-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,ありがとうございます
Dialogue: 1,0:03:10.99,0:03:12.42,JP-Main-Down,Resident,0,0,0,,こんにちは
Dialogue: 1,0:03:12.79,0:03:14.42,JP-Main-Down,Group,0,0,0,,こんにちは
Dialogue: 1,0:03:14.70,0:03:16.76,JP-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,感じのいい人たちばっかりだね
Dialogue: 1,0:03:16.76,0:03:18.24,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,吾野と大違い
Dialogue: 1,0:03:18.24,0:03:19.99,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,吾野は肉食大食て
Dialogue: 1,0:03:19.99,0:03:21.98,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,夏祭りが中心なったもんね
Dialogue: 1,0:03:21.98,0:03:25.51,JP-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,ああ　神社のお供えを何にするかでね
Dialogue: 1,0:03:25.51,0:03:27.73,JP-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,どっちでもいいじゃん　と思ったけど
Dialogue: 1,0:03:27.73,0:03:32.30,JP-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,吾野の名産なんだし　米とゴーヤと　中麦でいいのに
Dialogue: 1,0:03:32.30,0:03:33.76,JP-Main-Down,Keiko,0,0,0,,ゴーヤですか
Dialogue: 1,0:03:33.76,0:03:34.46,JP-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,あれ
Dialogue: 1,0:03:34.46,0:03:37.56,JP-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,松茸さん　もしかしてゴーヤ嫌いですか
Dialogue: 1,0:03:37.56,0:03:38.94,JP-Main-Down,Keiko,0,0,0,,あ　いいえ
Dialogue: 1,0:03:38.94,0:03:41.23,JP-Main-Down,Keiko,0,0,0,,そういうわけじゃないんですけど
Dialogue: 1,0:03:41.23,0:03:43.18,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,可愛くないよね
Dialogue: 1,0:03:43.18,0:03:45.66,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,だいたいゴーヤってズッキーニとかパプリカと　
Dialogue: 1,0:03:45.66,0:03:47.18,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,比べると田舎くさい
Dialogue: 1,0:03:47.18,0:03:48.65,JP-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,私は好きだけどな
Dialogue: 1,0:03:48.65,0:03:50.82,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,これだから晶は
Dialogue: 1,0:03:50.82,0:03:52.95,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,大丈夫かな私たち
Dialogue: 1,0:03:52.95,0:03:55.04,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,池袋みたいな台とかに行けるのかな
Dialogue: 1,0:03:55.04,0:03:57.82,JP-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,今はわかんないじゃん　どうなってるか
Dialogue: 1,0:03:57.11,0:04:00.41,JP-Main-up,Shizuru,0,0,0,,松茸さんって　池袋って行ったことあります
Dialogue: 1,0:04:00.83,0:04:04.67,JP-Main-Down,Keiko,0,0,0,,以前住んでいましたが　東吾野に戻ってきました
Dialogue: 1,0:04:04.67,0:04:05.61,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,いいな
Dialogue: 1,0:04:05.61,0:04:06.50,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,どんなとこ
Dialogue: 1,0:04:06.50,0:04:08.16,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,ここより都会なんでしょう
Dialogue: 1,0:04:08.16,0:04:09.28,JP-Main-Down,Keiko,0,0,0,,そうですね
Dialogue: 1,0:04:09.28,0:04:10.61,JP-Main-Down,Keiko,0,0,0,,そうだと思いますよ
Dialogue: 1,0:04:10.61,0:04:11.96,JP-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,思いますよ
Dialogue: 1,0:04:11.96,0:04:13.21,JP-Main-Down,Keiko,0,0,0,,ごめんなさい
Dialogue: 1,0:04:13.21,0:04:15.30,JP-Main-Down,Keiko,0,0,0,,今となってはもう興味がなくて
Dialogue: 1,0:04:15.56,0:04:18.03,JP-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,この子を見かけたこととかないですか
Dialogue: 1,0:04:18.03,0:04:19.65,JP-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,池袋あたりで
Dialogue: 1,0:04:19.65,0:04:20.47,JP-Main-Down,Keiko,0,0,0,,さあ
Dialogue: 1,0:04:20.47,0:04:22.69,JP-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,え　やっぱそうですよね
Dialogue: 1,0:04:26.56,0:04:28.36,JP-Main-Down,Yoka,0,0,0,,はい　できたよ
Dialogue: 1,0:04:28.36,0:04:30.05,JP-Main-Down,Yoka,0,0,0,,前髪それでいい
Dialogue: 1,0:04:30.05,0:04:30.99,JP-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,いい
Dialogue: 1,0:04:30.99,0:04:33.11,JP-Main-Down,Yoka,0,0,0,,もうちゃんと見てよ
Dialogue: 1,0:04:33.11,0:04:34.97,JP-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,葉香がいいならいいの
Dialogue: 1,0:04:35.78,0:04:36.67,JP-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,写真撮ろう
Dialogue: 1,0:04:36.93,0:04:38.38,JP-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,前髪記念だ
Dialogue: 1,0:04:43.81,0:04:45.19,JP-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,静留ちゃん
Dialogue: 1,0:04:45.19,0:04:46.44,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,何やってんの
Dialogue: 1,0:04:46.44,0:04:47.80,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,速く
Dialogue: 1,0:04:48.80,0:04:50.96,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,へえ　ちゃんとしてる
Dialogue: 1,0:04:50.96,0:04:51.77,JP-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,玲実ちゃん
Dialogue: 1,0:04:51.77,0:04:53.08,JP-Main-Down,Keiko,0,0,0,,そうなんです
Dialogue: 1,0:04:53.08,0:04:57.48,JP-Main-Down,Keiko,0,0,0,,東吾野では　お客様をもてなすことが大切だと考えています
Dialogue: 1,0:04:57.48,0:05:00.04,JP-Main-Down,Keiko,0,0,0,,特にミストサウナがおすすめですよ
Dialogue: 1,0:05:00.04,0:05:01.41,JP-Main-Down,Keiko,0,0,0,,おすすめっていうか
Dialogue: 1,0:05:01.41,0:05:02.97,JP-Main-Down,Keiko,0,0,0,,絶対ですから
Dialogue: 1,0:05:02.97,0:05:04.73,JP-Main-Down,Keiko,0,0,0,,必ず入ってくださいね
Dialogue: 1,0:05:04.73,0:05:05.81,JP-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,あ　はい
Dialogue: 1,0:05:06.12,0:05:07.72,JP-Main-Down,Keiko,0,0,0,,それじゃあ待ちほと
Dialogue: 1,0:05:10.15,0:05:12.48,JP-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,汗臭かったかな私たち
Dialogue: 1,0:05:12.48,0:05:14.28,JP-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,そもそもサウナってどこ
Dialogue: 1,0:05:14.88,0:05:15.87,JP-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,あれ
Dialogue: 1,0:05:15.87,0:05:17.83,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,へえ　おしゃれっぽい
Dialogue: 1,0:05:21.52,0:05:23.79,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,うわ　すごいミスト
Dialogue: 1,0:05:23.79,0:05:25.53,JP-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,いいね　入ろう入ろう
Dialogue: 1,0:05:25.53,0:05:27.45,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,デトックスって感じ
Dialogue: 1,0:05:28.01,0:05:29.21,JP-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,私はパス
Dialogue: 1,0:05:29.21,0:05:30.23,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,なんでよ
Dialogue: 1,0:05:30.23,0:05:33.30,JP-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,今のうちに服洗って乾かそうよ　晶ちゃん
Dialogue: 1,0:05:33.30,0:05:34.34,JP-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,いやいい
Dialogue: 1,0:05:34.34,0:05:37.10,JP-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,一人ならともかく　全員一緒とか無理
Dialogue: 1,0:05:37.10,0:05:38.20,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,分かった
Dialogue: 1,0:05:38.20,0:05:40.29,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,裸見られるのは恥ずかしいんでしょ
Dialogue: 1,0:05:40.29,0:05:41.97,JP-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,気にしなくていいのに
Dialogue: 1,0:05:41.97,0:05:43.33,JP-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,とにかくいい
Dialogue: 1,0:05:45.73,0:05:47.52,JP-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,なんかな
Dialogue: 1,0:05:47.52,0:05:50.44,JP-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,吾野出てきちゃってよかったのかな
Dialogue: 1,0:05:50.44,0:05:53.44,JP-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,でも一人で吾野なんてありえないし
Dialogue: 1,0:06:10.44,0:06:12.11,JP-Main-Down,Keiko,0,0,0,,失礼します
Dialogue: 1,0:06:12.40,0:06:15.55,JP-Main-Down,Keiko,0,0,0,,サウナに入ったら　お腹がすくんじゃないかと思って
Dialogue: 1,0:06:15.55,0:06:18.01,JP-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,あ　ありがとうございます
Dialogue: 1,0:06:21.57,0:06:22.80,JP-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,茸
Dialogue: 1,0:06:22.80,0:06:24.23,JP-Main-Down,Keiko,0,0,0,,お嫌いですか
Dialogue: 1,0:06:24.23,0:06:25.12,JP-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,え
Dialogue: 1,0:06:25.12,0:06:26.85,JP-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,あいいえ　全然
Dialogue: 1,0:06:26.85,0:06:28.30,JP-Main-Down,Keiko,0,0,0,,よかった
Dialogue: 1,0:06:28.30,0:06:30.43,JP-Main-Down,Keiko,0,0,0,,炊き込みご飯美味しいですよ
Dialogue: 1,0:06:30.43,0:06:32.25,JP-Main-Down,Keiko,0,0,0,,もつ茸ですから
Dialogue: 1,0:06:32.49,0:06:34.94,JP-Main-Down,Keiko,0,0,0,,ミストサウナはお入りになりました
Dialogue: 1,0:06:34.94,0:06:37.23,JP-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,あはい一応
Dialogue: 1,0:06:37.23,0:06:38.15,JP-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,若のみんなが
Dialogue: 1,0:06:38.15,0:06:40.23,JP-Main-Down,Keiko,0,0,0,,それはよかったです
