Dialogue: 1,0:20:35.80,0:20:38.15,JP-Main-Down,Keiko,0,0,0,,つうか　どうせ会えねえって
Dialogue: 1,0:20:38.15,0:20:39.86,JP-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,でもやっぱ行く
Dialogue: 1,0:20:39.86,0:20:42.00,JP-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,行って確かめないと納得できない
Dialogue: 1,0:20:42.00,0:20:43.68,JP-Main-Down,Keiko,0,0,0,,馬鹿じゃねえの
Dialogue: 1,0:20:43.68,0:20:45.97,JP-Main-Down,Keiko,0,0,0,,お前らはせいぜい惨めにあがいて
Dialogue: 1,0:20:45.97,0:20:48.30,JP-Main-Down,Keiko,0,0,0,,血反吐吐いて死にそうくなってやら
Dialogue: 1,0:20:48.30,0:20:49.63,JP-Main-Down,Keiko,0,0,0,,もう知らねえ
Dialogue: 1,0:20:54.13,0:20:55.14,JP-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,行こう
Dialogue: 1,0:20:57.49,0:20:59.60,JP-Main-Down,Keiko,0,0,0,,つっ　勝手にしな
Dialogue: 1,0:21:03.38,0:21:04.43,JP-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,あの
Dialogue: 1,0:21:04.43,0:21:06.67,JP-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,食料　ありがとう
Dialogue: 1,0:21:07.82,0:21:09.50,JP-Main-Down,Keiko,0,0,0,,知らねえよ
Dialogue: 1,0:21:24.71,0:21:26.42,JP-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,茸が
Dialogue: 1,0:21:26.78,0:21:28.94,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,どんな感じなんだろうね
Dialogue: 1,0:21:28.94,0:21:31.08,JP-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,玲実ちゃんちょっと生えてたよ
Dialogue: 1,0:21:31.08,0:21:32.39,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,撫子ちゃんだって
Dialogue: 1,0:21:33.77,0:21:35.44,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,もっとがっつり生えたら
Dialogue: 1,0:21:35.44,0:21:38.02,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,このまま死んじゃってもいいって思っちゃうのかな
Dialogue: 1,0:21:38.02,0:21:40.90,JP-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,たしかにちょっといい気分だったかもね
Dialogue: 1,0:21:40.90,0:21:42.29,JP-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,ふわふわって
Dialogue: 1,0:21:42.29,0:21:45.37,JP-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,なんか不思議っていうか　変な感じだった
Dialogue: 1,0:21:45.37,0:21:46.70,JP-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,ていうかさ
Dialogue: 1,0:21:46.70,0:21:48.92,JP-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,みんな私に感謝すべき
Dialogue: 1,0:21:48.92,0:21:49.82,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,感謝って
Dialogue: 1,0:21:49.82,0:21:51.31,JP-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,助けてあげたでしょ
Dialogue: 1,0:21:51.31,0:21:52.96,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,はいはい　感謝感謝
Dialogue: 1,0:21:52.96,0:21:54.17,JP-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,適当すぎる
Dialogue: 1,0:21:54.17,0:21:55.13,JP-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,うーちょっと
Dialogue: 1,0:21:55.13,0:21:56.38,JP-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,ぼっちさんまで失礼だ
Dialogue: 1,0:21:57.66,0:21:58.73,JP-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,どうしたの
Dialogue: 1,0:21:58.73,0:21:59.97,JP-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,なんでもない
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.55,ZH-Main-Down,,0,0,0,,OP前
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.55,0:00:03.23,ZH-Main-Down,Iguchi,0,0,0,,那么 就请介绍一下你自己吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.74,0:00:07.19,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,啊 好的 走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.41,0:00:09.62,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,啊 抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.62,0:00:10.59,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.59,0:00:12.54,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,欸 弄疼你了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.54,0:00:13.76,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,啊真的对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.76,0:00:14.35,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,你还好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.69,0:00:15.67,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,能站起来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.67,0:00:16.41,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,站起来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.32,0:00:19.89,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,诶
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.89,0:00:22.50,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,中富同学长得挺漂亮呀
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.08,0:00:24.71,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,静留嘴真甜
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.71,0:00:26.19,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,呐 我叫玲实
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.19,0:00:28.26,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,直接叫我玲实就好啦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.26,0:00:29.36,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,啊 就是本名
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.36,0:00:31.37,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,真正的名字叫零分玲实
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.37,0:00:32.47,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,完全不是
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.47,0:00:34.35,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,中富同学 是不是很惊讶呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.58,0:00:36.03,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,不用害怕的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.03,0:00:37.09,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,不会吃掉你的
Comment: 0,0:02:13.50,0:02:15.50,ZH-Main-Down,,0,0,0,,正文
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.50,0:02:18.52,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,大家是东吾野的居民吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.52,0:02:19.63,ZH-Main-Down,Keiko,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.63,0:02:21.14,ZH-Main-Down,Keiko,0,0,0,,这个是列车吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.14,0:02:22.36,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,是的 这是列车
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.36,0:02:24.31,ZH-Main-Down,Keiko,0,0,0,,好久没有见到了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.31,0:02:26.70,ZH-Main-Down,Keiko,0,0,0,,各位是从哪里来到这里的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.13,0:02:28.53,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,隔壁吾野来的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.86,0:02:30.06,ZH-Main-Down,Resident,0,0,0,,原来是吾野
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.41,0:02:31.92,ZH-Main-Down,Resident,0,0,0,,吾野啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.37,0:02:33.78,ZH-Main-Down,Keiko,0,0,0,,那可真是难得
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.78,0:02:35.95,ZH-Main-Down,Keiko,0,0,0,,吾野现在距离这里很远的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.95,0:02:37.71,ZH-Main-Down,Keiko,0,0,0,,一路上很辛苦吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.71,0:02:39.46,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,啊 还行吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.46,0:02:41.51,ZH-Main-Down,Keiko,0,0,0,,吾野的大家还好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.23,0:02:44.95,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,好倒是挺好的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.95,0:02:46.39,ZH-Main-Down,Keiko,0,0,0,,务必培养
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.39,0:02:49.81,ZH-Main-Down,Keiko,0,0,0,,不对 请让我们尽地主之仪吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.81,0:02:54.07,ZH-Main-Down,Keiko,0,0,0,,好在在东吾野 人口相对较少
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.07,0:02:55.92,ZH-Main-Down,Keiko,0,0,0,,家里有许多空置的房间
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.92,0:02:57.36,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,好耶 帮大忙了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.36,0:02:57.98,ZH-Main-Down,Keiko,0,0,0,,务必前来
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.98,0:02:58.72,ZH-Main-up,Resident,0,0,0,,是呀
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.22,0:02:59.24,ZH-Main-Down,Resident,0,0,0,,是呀是呀
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.24,0:03:02.45,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,但是我们带的钱并不多
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.45,0:03:04.45,ZH-Main-Down,Keiko,0,0,0,,这点小钱不用介意啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.45,0:03:05.36,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,好耶
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.36,0:03:07.06,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,非常感谢您
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.99,0:03:12.42,ZH-Main-Down,Resident,0,0,0,,您好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.79,0:03:14.42,ZH-Main-Down,Group,0,0,0,,您好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.70,0:03:16.76,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,感觉这里的人都很友好呀
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.76,0:03:18.24,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,和吾野相比大相径庭
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.24,0:03:19.99,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,吾野都是肉食贪吃的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.99,0:03:21.98,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,夏日祭的核心都是吃吃吃
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.98,0:03:25.51,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,确实 神社的供奉会放什么东西呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.51,0:03:27.73,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,咱认为想放啥都问题不大
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.73,0:03:32.30,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,用吾野的特产明明挺好 比如大米 苦瓜 中筋小麦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.30,0:03:33.76,ZH-Main-Down,Keiko,0,0,0,,苦瓜啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.76,0:03:34.46,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,啊嘞
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.46,0:03:37.56,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,松茸小姐 难道您不喜欢苦瓜吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.56,0:03:38.94,ZH-Main-Down,Keiko,0,0,0,,啊 并不是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.94,0:03:41.23,ZH-Main-Down,Keiko,0,0,0,,我不是这个意思
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.23,0:03:43.18,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,毕竟它并不可爱嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.18,0:03:45.66,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,再说 苦瓜与西葫芦 还有辣椒相比
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.66,0:03:47.18,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,真的太土里土气了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.18,0:03:48.65,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,但是我挺喜欢的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.65,0:03:50.82,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,也就只有小晶你了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.82,0:03:52.95,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,我们应该没问题的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.95,0:03:55.04,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,我们到底能否抵达池袋呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.04,0:03:57.82,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,现在我们根本不知道 会发生什么事情
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.11,0:04:00.41,ZH-Main-up,Shizuru,0,0,0,,松茸小姐 您有去过池袋吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.83,0:04:04.67,ZH-Main-Down,Keiko,0,0,0,,以前我住在那里 但后来又回来东吾野这了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.67,0:04:05.61,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,挺好呀
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.61,0:04:06.50,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,那里怎么样呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.50,0:04:08.16,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,比这里更加城市化对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.16,0:04:09.28,ZH-Main-Down,Keiko,0,0,0,,我想是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.28,0:04:10.61,ZH-Main-Down,Keiko,0,0,0,,我认为是这样的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.61,0:04:11.96,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,认为的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.96,0:04:13.21,ZH-Main-Down,Keiko,0,0,0,,实在对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.21,0:04:15.30,ZH-Main-Down,Keiko,0,0,0,,现在的我已经对它不感兴趣了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.56,0:04:18.03,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,这个女孩 你有见到过她 或者类似她的人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.03,0:04:19.65,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,在池袋那里
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.65,0:04:20.47,ZH-Main-Down,Keiko,0,0,0,,不清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.47,0:04:22.69,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,唉 果然是这样的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.56,0:04:28.36,ZH-Main-Down,Yoka,0,0,0,,好 剪好啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.36,0:04:30.05,ZH-Main-Down,Yoka,0,0,0,,前刘海这样可以吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.05,0:04:30.99,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,挺好挺好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.99,0:04:33.11,ZH-Main-Down,Yoka,0,0,0,,真的是 好好看看啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.11,0:04:34.97,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,葉香剪的头发没有不好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.78,0:04:36.67,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,来拍张照片吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.93,0:04:38.38,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,纪念一下它
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.81,0:04:45.19,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,静留
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.19,0:04:46.44,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,你在做啥
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.44,0:04:47.80,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,快点
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.80,0:04:50.96,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,诶 挺正式的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.96,0:04:51.77,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,玲实
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.77,0:04:53.08,ZH-Main-Down,Keiko,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.08,0:04:57.48,ZH-Main-Down,Keiko,0,0,0,,东吾野这里宾至如归
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.48,0:05:00.04,ZH-Main-Down,Keiko,0,0,0,,特别是水雾桑拿很推荐噢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.04,0:05:01.41,ZH-Main-Down,Keiko,0,0,0,,说起推荐的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.41,0:05:02.97,ZH-Main-Down,Keiko,0,0,0,,绝对要试一试
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.97,0:05:04.73,ZH-Main-Down,Keiko,0,0,0,,请务必蒸一蒸
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.73,0:05:05.81,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,啊 好的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.12,0:05:07.72,ZH-Main-Down,Keiko,0,0,0,,那么请您稍等片刻
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.15,0:05:12.48,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,我们是不是有汗臭味了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.48,0:05:14.28,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,但说起来 桑拿在哪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.88,0:05:15.87,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,那里吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.87,0:05:17.83,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,诶 挺精致的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.52,0:05:23.79,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,哇 好厉害的水雾
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.79,0:05:25.53,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,挺好的 快进去快进去
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.53,0:05:27.45,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,感觉就像排毒一样
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.01,0:05:29.21,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,我就算了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.21,0:05:30.23,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,为啥啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.23,0:05:33.30,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,现在正好洗洗衣服顺带晾干呀 小晶
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.30,0:05:34.34,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,不 我不用了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.34,0:05:37.10,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,先不说一个人 全部人一起洗我做不到
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.10,0:05:38.20,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,我明白啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.20,0:05:40.29,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,裸体被别人看到会很害羞的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.29,0:05:41.97,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,明明不用这么在意的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.97,0:05:43.33,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,总而言之你们洗就好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.73,0:05:47.52,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,总感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.52,0:05:50.44,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,从吾野出来到底是不是好事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.44,0:05:53.44,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,但是一个人在吾野呆着也不行
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.44,0:06:12.11,ZH-Main-Down,Keiko,0,0,0,,打扰一下
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.40,0:06:15.55,ZH-Main-Down,Keiko,0,0,0,,蒸完桑拿后 我想你们肚子应该会很饿吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.55,0:06:18.01,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,啊 感谢您的款待
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.57,0:06:22.80,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,蘑菇
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.80,0:06:24.23,ZH-Main-Down,Keiko,0,0,0,,您不喜欢吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.23,0:06:25.12,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,诶
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.12,0:06:26.85,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,啊并不 还行
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.85,0:06:28.30,ZH-Main-Down,Keiko,0,0,0,,太好啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.30,0:06:30.43,ZH-Main-Down,Keiko,0,0,0,,就着煮熟的米饭会很好吃的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.43,0:06:32.25,ZH-Main-Down,Keiko,0,0,0,,毕竟这是松茸呀
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.49,0:06:34.94,ZH-Main-Down,Keiko,0,0,0,,您有享受过水雾桑拿了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.94,0:06:37.23,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,啊有 大概蒸了蒸
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.23,0:06:38.15,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,和其她人一起
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.15,0:06:40.23,ZH-Main-Down,Keiko,0,0,0,,这真的太好啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.23,0:06:42.84,ZH-Main-Down,Keiko,0,0,0,,今天请好好休息一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.84,0:06:45.04,ZH-Main-Down,Keiko,0,0,0,,轻轻松松的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.04,0:06:45.86,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,感谢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.37,0:06:56.85,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,小晶这些是什么 盛宴啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.85,0:06:58.16,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,发生什么了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.16,0:07:00.84,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,刚才松茸小姐拿过来的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.14,0:07:02.83,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,真的无微不至呀
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.83,0:07:05.38,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,刚刚蒸完桑拿 肚子一下子就饿了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.38,0:07:06.59,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,我们一起吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.59,0:07:08.08,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,我要吃「猪肉卷明天见」
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.08,0:07:09.12,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.48,0:07:10.31,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.31,0:07:11.41,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,这不奇怪吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.41,0:07:12.01,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,奇怪啥
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.01,0:07:12.98,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,这里的人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.98,0:07:14.10,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,诶 是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.10,0:07:15.11,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,不挺亲切的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.11,0:07:16.45,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,除了头上长着蘑菇
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.45,0:07:17.21,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,就是这个
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.21,0:07:18.50,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,为什么长着蘑菇
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.50,0:07:19.30,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,问问他们呗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.30,0:07:21.13,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,这样不行
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.13,0:07:21.96,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,诶 为啥
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.96,0:07:22.89,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,啊是那个
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.89,0:07:25.92,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,好比如 说别人秃头的自己也是秃头
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.92,0:07:27.32,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,礼貌 礼仪
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.32,0:07:28.23,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,原来是这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.23,0:07:29.10,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,不是这样的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.10,0:07:31.17,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,长着蘑菇也没啥问题吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.17,0:07:33.69,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,吾野的可都是动物啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.69,0:07:35.86,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,这里的人到不会整天嚷嚷吃肉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.86,0:07:36.90,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,而且还挺友善的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.90,0:07:38.83,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,东吾野确实是个好地方
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.83,0:07:40.43,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,太悠闲了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.11,0:07:57.30,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,玲实
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.30,0:07:58.85,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,呐 玲实醒醒
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.85,0:08:01.64,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,你个零分玲实
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.60,0:08:05.88,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,我也能一个人去厕所
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.77,0:08:14.26,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,为啥桑拿会给一个单独的房间
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.26,0:08:16.24,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,而厕所离得那么远
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.24,0:08:17.94,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,设计好奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.11,0:08:24.63,ZH-Main-Down,Resident,0,0,0,,翘首以盼了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.63,0:08:26.11,ZH-Main-Down,Resident,0,0,0,,都睡那了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.64,0:08:37.60,ZH-Main-Down,Resident,0,0,0,,果然外来的人真是笨蛋啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.60,0:08:38.98,ZH-Main-Down,Resident,0,0,0,,毫无怀疑
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.98,0:08:40.43,ZH-Main-Down,Resident,0,0,0,,正如所你所说一样
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.43,0:08:41.67,ZH-Main-Down,Resident,0,0,0,,快点开始吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.67,0:08:43.44,ZH-Main-Down,Resident,0,0,0,,越早来越好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.44,0:08:45.46,ZH-Main-Down,Keiko,0,0,0,,让她们成为我们的「伙伴」吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.46,0:08:48.49,ZH-Main-Down,Resident,0,0,0,,这对她们来说是最好的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.49,0:08:50.38,ZH-Main-Down,Resident,0,0,0,,我们这群「人」要拯救她们
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.00,0:08:54.55,ZH-Main-Down,Resident,0,0,0,,是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.50,0:09:13.65,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,怎么了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.02,0:09:18.44,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,静留
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.26,0:09:21.11,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,我都惊醒了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.11,0:09:21.96,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,怎么了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.27,0:09:31.45,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,松茸小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.78,0:09:35.42,ZH-Main-Down,Keiko,0,0,0,,毕竟是在陌生的地方 定是做了个噩梦吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.42,0:09:37.33,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,得了吧让我好好休息会
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.33,0:09:39.30,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,小晶 快点给松茸小姐道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.57,0:09:42.26,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,大声吵闹 快点说声对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.26,0:09:43.85,ZH-Main-Down,Keiko,0,0,0,,没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.85,0:09:45.69,ZH-Main-Down,Keiko,0,0,0,,请好好休息吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.01,0:09:49.09,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,再回笼睡觉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.09,0:09:50.81,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,这里 真的很可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.81,0:09:52.18,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,早点离开这里吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.18,0:09:53.54,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,你在说啥啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.54,0:09:55.06,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,小晶真的是个胆小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.06,0:09:56.30,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.30,0:09:57.72,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,我才不是害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.72,0:09:59.77,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,你和她一起睡觉吧 玲实
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.77,0:10:00.52,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,哈 不要
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.52,0:10:02.15,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,小晶睡相很不好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.15,0:10:04.06,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,小晶我陪你去厕所吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.06,0:10:05.68,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,你还没有去对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.68,0:10:06.79,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.31,0:10:08.62,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,在吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.62,0:10:09.92,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,我在的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.92,0:10:12.12,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,不要乱走动 抚子
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.12,0:10:13.50,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.16,0:10:18.02,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,看不见星星啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.38,0:10:20.45,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,明天也是阴天吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.18,0:10:25.83,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,你们都被骗了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.83,0:10:27.23,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,是阴谋论啦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.23,0:10:29.61,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,小晶很喜欢「控济会」嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.61,0:10:30.81,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,是「共济会」
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.81,0:10:32.06,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.06,0:10:33.43,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,我们马上就离开了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.36,0:10:37.54,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,啊敲
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.54,0:10:38.83,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,就一个晚上吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.83,0:10:40.37,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,是不是光照太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.37,0:10:41.53,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,不会啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.53,0:10:42.71,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,一直都是阴云天气
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.71,0:10:45.65,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,还有 这里和吾野相比更加潮湿
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.65,0:10:47.87,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,结果 它们看起来长得挺健壮的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.87,0:10:49.24,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,啊 果实已经成熟了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.18,0:10:55.61,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,这个苦味可是很有营养的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.17,0:10:58.54,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,感觉你们的反应挺大的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.54,0:10:59.91,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,诶 为啥
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.91,0:11:01.97,ZH-Main-Down,Keiko,0,0,0,,毕竟 在阳光的直射下
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.97,0:11:04.64,ZH-Main-Down,Keiko,0,0,0,,全部的生物都会产生不良的影响
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.64,0:11:05.88,ZH-Main-Down,Keiko,0,0,0,,又热 又干燥
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.88,0:11:08.64,ZH-Main-Down,Keiko,0,0,0,,被光照烧死是宇宙不变的定律
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.64,0:11:09.89,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,哈
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.89,0:11:12.11,ZH-Main-Down,Keiko,0,0,0,,然而这个 还能健康茁壮成长
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.11,0:11:14.24,ZH-Main-Down,Keiko,0,0,0,,就是这样瞧不起我们
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.24,0:11:17.11,ZH-Main-Down,Keiko,0,0,0,,就像这样 就因为存在玉米还有阳光之类的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.11,0:11:19.07,ZH-Main-Down,Keiko,0,0,0,,世界已经变得非常奇怪了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.07,0:11:20.37,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,那个
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.37,0:11:24.38,ZH-Main-Down,Keiko,0,0,0,,总而言之这些苦 全部都给我扯下来
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.38,0:11:25.76,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,啊 行
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.76,0:11:26.98,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,我就打算这么做
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.98,0:11:28.05,ZH-Main-Down,Keiko,0,0,0,,令人恐惧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.04,0:11:31.86,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,原来她这么讨厌
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.86,0:11:34.85,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,总而言之 先把这些全部都摘下来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.85,0:11:36.37,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,感觉像是一个阴谋
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.37,0:11:38.46,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,阴谋 是啥 谁的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.46,0:11:40.97,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,是为了阻碍我们不让离开
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.97,0:11:42.59,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,你又开始说胡话了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.59,0:11:43.50,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,这才不是胡话
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.75,0:11:44.55,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,小晶
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.55,0:11:46.64,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,和我一起对抗苦瓜吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.64,0:11:49.47,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,这期间 玲实和抚子去买点东西吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.47,0:11:50.16,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,欸
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.16,0:11:52.78,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,有能够长期保存的食物会更好呀
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.78,0:11:53.95,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,很危险的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.95,0:11:54.93,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.93,0:11:56.59,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,很多事情要留个心眼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.59,0:11:57.66,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,抚子
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.66,0:11:59.65,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,东吾野有便利店吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.65,0:12:00.46,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,挺有趣的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.46,0:12:01.14,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,玲实
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.14,0:12:02.47,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.03,0:12:07.41,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,静 玲 抚
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.33,0:12:13.69,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,你们在想什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.69,0:12:15.41,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,不行 不能这样的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.41,0:12:16.64,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,又为啥
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.64,0:12:18.50,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,那边就拜托你了 小晶
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.50,0:12:20.72,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,我们不是说要去池袋吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.72,0:12:21.72,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,会去的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.72,0:12:23.34,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,那你是为什么缺乏信心
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.34,0:12:26.35,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,为什么会如此乐不思蜀我根本不明白啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.84,0:12:29.82,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,我去找她们俩
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.75,0:12:42.06,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,这是什么鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.06,0:12:43.09,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,惨了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.83,0:12:56.14,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,玲实 抚子
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.14,0:12:58.06,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,他们说免费给我们
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.06,0:12:59.85,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,真的可以吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.85,0:13:02.16,ZH-Main-Down,Keiko,0,0,0,,我们已经不再需要它们了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.16,0:13:02.84,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,已经
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.12,0:13:07.59,ZH-Main-Down,Keiko,0,0,0,,你 你们比起我们更加需要这些东西
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.59,0:13:09.73,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,哇 超级亲切的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.73,0:13:12.33,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,有了这些的话 生存暂时是没什么问题了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.33,0:13:15.20,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,就算对我们这么好 也不能回报些什么给你们
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.20,0:13:16.96,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,我们马上就要离开了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.96,0:13:20.30,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,和吾野的不同 东吾野的大家更为亲切
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.30,0:13:21.44,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,而且还很冷静
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.44,0:13:23.10,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,博爱精神都满溢了出来
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.10,0:13:25.29,ZH-Main-Down,Keiko,0,0,0,,这些东西没什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.29,0:13:27.24,ZH-Main-Down,Keiko,0,0,0,,曾经的东吾野
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.24,0:13:31.44,ZH-Main-Down,Keiko,0,0,0,,很多人也是沮丧担心
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.44,0:13:34.36,ZH-Main-Down,Keiko,0,0,0,,但是 7G事件后我们察觉到了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.82,0:13:38.03,ZH-Main-Down,Keiko,0,0,0,,比起面朝黄土背朝天
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.03,0:13:42.32,ZH-Main-Down,Keiko,0,0,0,,更好的生活 便是在短暂的人生中充实享受时间
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.45,0:13:47.62,ZH-Main-Down,Keiko,0,0,0,,如此决定后 再也不会忍气吞声了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.97,0:13:50.68,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,挺深奥的呀 松茸小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.68,0:13:53.88,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,这种心境 我们是否也能领悟到呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.88,0:13:55.92,ZH-Main-Down,Keiko,0,0,0,,会的 肯定能理解的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.92,0:13:58.36,ZH-Main-Down,Keiko,0,0,0,,你们大家 很快就会的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.70,0:14:00.34,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,呐
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.34,0:14:01.82,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,快点走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.82,0:14:03.74,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,静留她肯定会担心我们的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.74,0:14:05.78,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,担心 为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.78,0:14:08.56,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,好想成为像松茸小姐一样的存在呀
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.56,0:14:10.89,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,不行 我们必须要去池袋
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.89,0:14:12.64,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,欸 池袋
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.64,0:14:14.26,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,东吾野这不好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.26,0:14:15.24,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,也不错呀
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.24,0:14:16.40,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,不行的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.40,0:14:18.89,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,我们必须要去见葉香的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.21,0:14:23.49,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,静留
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.49,0:14:24.67,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,苦瓜根本没有修剪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.67,0:14:26.10,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,苦瓜
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.10,0:14:27.50,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,啊 苦瓜
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.85,0:14:31.13,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,这样做有什么意义所在吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.13,0:14:31.86,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,啥
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.86,0:14:34.80,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,我们真的能去到池袋吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.80,0:14:36.87,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,感觉我们根本到不了那里
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.87,0:14:38.03,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,你在说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.03,0:14:39.87,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,不是昨天才出来的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.87,0:14:43.41,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,就算到了那里 感觉也不会改变什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.41,0:14:45.89,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,你不是说必须要见到葉香吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.89,0:14:49.80,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,嗯 就算一直等她也无所谓了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.80,0:14:52.96,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,再者说她也不一定记得我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.96,0:14:55.21,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,见都没见到根本不知道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.21,0:14:55.99,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,你们俩
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.99,0:14:57.99,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,玲实和抚子你们也说点什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.99,0:14:59.01,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,想睡
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.87,0:15:04.08,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,小晶你太吵了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.08,0:15:07.12,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,不是饿殍满地 孤苦伶仃地活着
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.12,0:15:10.45,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,昙花一现 乐天知命才是真理啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.17,0:15:14.49,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,已经不行了 完蛋了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.98,0:15:15.89,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,五点
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.20,0:15:21.99,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,这里是小晶 现在在东吾野
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.26,0:15:25.93,ZH-Main-Down,Zenjiro,0,0,0,,这里是吾野 报告状况
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.36,0:15:27.71,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,蘑菇很多
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.71,0:15:28.87,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,遍地都是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.87,0:15:30.45,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,请教蘑菇的危险程度
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.90,0:15:32.71,ZH-Main-Down,Zenjiro,0,0,0,,什么 蘑菇吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.71,0:15:33.40,ZH-Main-Down,Zenjiro,0,0,0,,交给我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.40,0:15:36.25,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,香浓松茸 鲜美占地
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.25,0:15:38.55,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,松露菌不是猪而是狗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.55,0:15:39.87,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,白色比黑色
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.22,0:15:44.51,ZH-Main-Down,Zenjiro,0,0,0,,总而言之 蘑菇就是圆圆的 通常为环形东西
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.51,0:15:47.63,ZH-Main-Down,Zenjiro,0,0,0,,据说这是一个关于妖精和魔女的死亡传言
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.63,0:15:51.30,ZH-Main-Down,Zenjiro,0,0,0,,实际上菌类的生长与死亡相伴 很容易就能观察到
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.30,0:15:54.98,ZH-Main-Down,Zenjiro,0,0,0,,据说雷击之后很容易出现这种情况 就是所谓的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.98,0:15:56.89,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,谁他妈管你打不打雷
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.89,0:15:59.38,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,快点告诉我避免或是逃离蘑菇侵害的方法
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.38,0:16:01.88,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,把蘑菇给吃光 吧吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.88,0:16:03.89,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,吧吧吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.44,0:16:10.29,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,不要将重要的情报消耗在吃蘑菇身上啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.80,0:16:21.77,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,苦瓜
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.51,0:16:24.88,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,不要过来
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.86,0:16:29.58,ZH-Main-Down,Resident,0,0,0,,为什么要反抗呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.58,0:16:31.60,ZH-Main-Down,Resident,0,0,0,,直接过来这不好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.60,0:16:32.59,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,别废话
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.59,0:16:35.14,ZH-Main-Down,Resident,0,0,0,,如今你苟且偷生 又有什么好处
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.14,0:16:37.81,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,变成蘑菇才是一种损失
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.81,0:16:38.83,ZH-Main-Down,King Oyster,0,0,0,,没关系的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.83,0:16:40.26,ZH-Main-Down,King Oyster,0,0,0,,蘑菇可没有烦恼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.26,0:16:41.80,ZH-Main-Down,Enoki,0,0,0,,蘑菇也没有痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.80,0:16:43.64,ZH-Main-Down,Fly Agaric,0,0,0,,蘑菇还不用思考
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.99,0:16:46.36,ZH-Main-Down,Group,0,0,0,,大家都变成蘑菇吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.36,0:16:47.44,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,绝对不行
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.74,0:16:49.15,ZH-Main-Down,Resident,0,0,0,,很开心的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.78,0:16:54.65,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,蘑菇
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.65,0:16:55.81,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,蘑菇军团
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.57,0:17:02.92,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,小晶你太吵了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.92,0:17:04.70,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,好想轻轻松松地离开呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.70,0:17:08.08,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,什么也不用想 轻飘飘的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.08,0:17:09.66,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,别光蹲在那啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.66,0:17:12.14,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,你们说去池袋到底是为了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.14,0:17:13.10,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,池袋
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.10,0:17:16.13,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,难道你不是去池袋赶潮流的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.13,0:17:17.26,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,时尚
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.26,0:17:19.38,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,难道不是为了去见葉香吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.65,0:17:21.85,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,葉香
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.85,0:17:25.79,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,根本不是在这 给它们培养蘑菇的时候啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.75,0:17:27.78,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,葉香
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.40,0:17:33.86,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,葉香什么的 自顾自就离开吾野了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.86,0:17:35.69,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,自顾自地消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.69,0:17:37.21,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,她怎样都无所谓了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.21,0:17:38.38,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,你在说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.38,0:17:39.82,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,她是「朋友」才对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.82,0:17:41.55,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.55,0:17:43.53,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,到底是不是朋友呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.83,0:17:46.81,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,分别的时候我们也还不是朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.81,0:17:49.46,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,再说了葉香所想的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.75,0:17:52.63,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,我根本一点也不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.91,0:17:57.05,ZH-Main-Down,Yoka,0,0,0,,静留 学习有助于培养情操
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.05,0:17:59.64,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,欸 损人也不错
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.99,0:18:04.40,ZH-Main-Down,Yoka,0,0,0,,未来发展意向的调查问卷还没出来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.40,0:18:05.96,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,前途啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.96,0:18:07.53,ZH-Main-Down,Yoka,0,0,0,,有没想要成为的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.53,0:18:08.47,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,有的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.47,0:18:10.01,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,想要成为非常明智的人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.01,0:18:12.02,ZH-Main-Down,Yoka,0,0,0,,那可要好好学习
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.02,0:18:13.37,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,还要学习啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.73,0:18:17.05,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,葉香呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.05,0:18:17.73,ZH-Main-Down,Yoka,0,0,0,,有的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.73,0:18:19.17,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,什么 快说快说
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.17,0:18:20.50,ZH-Main-Down,Yoka,0,0,0,,我想去池袋
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.50,0:18:23.91,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,你别骗我 去那坐列车就到了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.91,0:18:27.59,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,我要不要成为吾野柔术综合格斗家呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.59,0:18:29.69,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,而且 还想和食蚁兽打一架
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.69,0:18:30.82,ZH-Main-Down,Yoka,0,0,0,,不挺好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.82,0:18:32.31,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,好好回答我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.31,0:18:33.93,ZH-Main-Down,Yoka,0,0,0,,好好回答啦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.68,0:18:35.83,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,葉香
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.83,0:18:37.00,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,对啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.00,0:18:39.54,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,葉香会在池袋等着你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.54,0:18:43.32,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,池袋 葉香 等着我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.06,0:18:50.95,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.25,0:18:51.10,ZH-Main-up,Shiitake,0,0,0,,快住手
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.10,0:18:52.40,ZH-Main-Down,Enoki,0,0,0,,别这样 快放手
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.30,0:18:59.70,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,到底是否会变得糟糕 取决于我们 自己
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.70,0:19:02.39,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,静留
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.28,0:19:06.79,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,你谁
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.25,0:19:09.56,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,开个玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.56,0:19:11.02,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,稍微来点轻松与关爱
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.84,0:19:13.17,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,抱歉抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.17,0:19:15.36,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,一起拔掉抚子和玲实的蘑菇吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.36,0:19:15.92,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.92,0:19:18.38,ZH-Main-Down,King Oyster,0,0,0,,难道你们不懂得幸福吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.12,0:19:19.15,ZH-Main-up,Porcini,0,0,0,,我们要守护我们的伙伴
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.15,0:19:22.18,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,别擅自把我们变成你的伙伴
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.28,0:19:26.25,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,啊嘞
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.25,0:19:28.85,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,我们 到底怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.53,0:19:31.53,ZH-Main-Down,Group,0,0,0,,蘑菇 蘑菇
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.80,0:19:34.29,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,各位 你们被蘑菇占据了思想
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.29,0:19:34.98,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,要怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.98,0:19:37.66,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,就算要逃跑 但被这么多人围着
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.09,0:19:40.44,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,苦瓜
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.44,0:19:41.50,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,难不成
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.49,0:19:44.96,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,剩下的交给我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.96,0:19:45.59,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,诶诶
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.59,0:19:46.37,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,等会
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.37,0:19:50.20,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,苦瓜
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.35,0:19:55.67,ZH-Main-Down,Keiko,0,0,0,,不要 请快点住手
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.67,0:19:59.68,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,被蘑菇寄生 成为它们的一员真的好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.68,0:20:02.91,ZH-Main-Down,Keiko,0,0,0,,不要 别揪着老娘不放
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.24,0:20:05.17,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,那个
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.17,0:20:05.85,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,松茸小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.85,0:20:07.56,ZH-Main-Down,Keiko,0,0,0,,你这人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.56,0:20:08.90,ZH-Main-Down,Keiko,0,0,0,,啊真的是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.90,0:20:10.75,ZH-Main-Down,Keiko,0,0,0,,别搁这碍手碍脚的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.75,0:20:12.76,ZH-Main-Down,Keiko,0,0,0,,明明那么亲切帮助你们
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.76,0:20:14.12,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,亲切
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.12,0:20:17.05,ZH-Main-Down,Keiko,0,0,0,,我们大家是喜欢蘑菇才成为的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.05,0:20:19.22,ZH-Main-Down,Keiko,0,0,0,,这个没有未来的狗屎世界
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.22,0:20:20.45,ZH-Main-Down,Keiko,0,0,0,,比起活几十年
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.45,0:20:23.22,ZH-Main-Down,Keiko,0,0,0,,不如像蘑菇一样 开心 嬉皮 并蜗居
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.22,0:20:26.16,ZH-Main-Down,Keiko,0,0,0,,并在一两年后就死去
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.16,0:20:28.24,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,一两年后就死去
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.24,0:20:30.43,ZH-Main-Down,Keiko,0,0,0,,想去池袋什么的 要怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.43,0:20:31.28,ZH-Main-Down,Keiko,0,0,0,,不行不行
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.56,0:20:34.60,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,我只是有个朋友 想见她
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.60,0:20:35.80,ZH-Main-Down,Keiko,0,0,0,,见了又如何
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.80,0:20:38.15,ZH-Main-Down,Keiko,0,0,0,,不如说 你永远也见不到她
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.15,0:20:39.86,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,但是我还要去
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.86,0:20:42.00,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,必须要去看看 才能接受与否
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.00,0:20:43.68,ZH-Main-Down,Keiko,0,0,0,,你是笨蛋吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.68,0:20:45.97,ZH-Main-Down,Keiko,0,0,0,,你们这群人只不过是在苦苦挣扎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.97,0:20:48.30,ZH-Main-Down,Keiko,0,0,0,,最终会口吐鲜血 然后死去
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.30,0:20:49.63,ZH-Main-Down,Keiko,0,0,0,,Who cares?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.13,0:20:55.14,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,出发吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.49,0:20:59.60,ZH-Main-Down,Keiko,0,0,0,,切 自以为是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.38,0:21:04.43,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,那个
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.43,0:21:06.67,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,感谢您能给予我们食物与水
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.82,0:21:09.50,ZH-Main-Down,Keiko,0,0,0,,菇不在乎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.71,0:21:26.42,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,蘑菇啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.78,0:21:28.94,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,会是什么样的感觉呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.94,0:21:31.08,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,玲实你稍微长大了一点呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.08,0:21:32.39,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,抚子也是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.77,0:21:35.44,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,如果它生长得更茁壮
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.44,0:21:38.02,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,我不知道会不会就这么被死亡
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.02,0:21:40.90,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,但感觉确实挺好的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.90,0:21:42.29,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,轻飘飘的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.29,0:21:45.37,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,感觉有些不可思议 或是感觉怪怪的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.37,0:21:46.70,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,要我说
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.70,0:21:48.92,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,大家都应该感谢我
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.92,0:21:49.82,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,感谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.82,0:21:51.31,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,毕竟我拯救了你们
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.31,0:21:52.96,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,啊对对 感谢你感谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.96,0:21:54.17,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,太随便了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.17,0:21:55.13,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,欸等会
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.13,0:21:56.38,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,波奇你太无礼了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.66,0:21:58.73,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,怎么了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.73,0:21:59.97,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,没什么
